---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Marcas - Tienda de Suplementos">

	
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-blue-900 to-indigo-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
			<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="mb-6">
						<span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide backdrop-blur-sm border border-yellow-400/30">
							Marcas Premium
						</span>
					</div>
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-blue-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
						Las Mejores Marcas
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						Trabajamos exclusivamente con las marcas más reconocidas y confiables de la industria mundial.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
						<button class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
							Explorar Marcas
						</button>
						<button class="border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm">
							Marca del Mes
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- Featured Brands -->
		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Marcas Destacadas</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">ON</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">Optimum Nutrition</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">45 productos</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">DYM</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">Dymatize</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">32 productos</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">MT</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">MuscleTech</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">28 productos</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">BSN</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">BSN</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">24 productos</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">C4</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">Cellucor</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">20 productos</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
						<div class="h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-bold text-lg">UNI</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-semibold">Universal</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">18 productos</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Brand Spotlight -->
		<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Marca del Mes</h2>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
						<div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
							<div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-4 rounded-lg inline-block mb-6">
								<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">OPTIMUM NUTRITION</h3>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Gold Standard - La Proteína #1 del Mundo</h4>
							<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
								Optimum Nutrition ha sido líder en suplementación deportiva por más de 30 años. 
								Su producto estrella, Gold Standard 100% Whey, es la proteína más vendida globalmente.
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Calidad superior garantizada
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Certificaciones internacionales
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Respaldado por atletas profesionales
								</li>
							</ul>
							<button class="bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
								Ver Productos ON
							</button>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-200 p-8 lg:p-12 flex items-center justify-center">
							<div class="text-center">
								<div class="w-48 h-48 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
									<span class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">[LOGO ON]</span>
								</div>
								<p class="text-blue-800 font-semibold">Desde 1986 - Calidad Comprobada</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- All Brands Grid -->
		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Todas Nuestras Marcas</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">MT</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">MuscleTech</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Innovación científica</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Líder en investigación y desarrollo de suplementos deportivos de alta tecnología.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">28 productos</span>
							<button class="text-red-500 font-semibold hover:text-red-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">BSN</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">BSN</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Resultados extremos</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Conocida por sus fórmulas potentes y sabores únicos que revolucionaron la industria.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">24 productos</span>
							<button class="text-purple-500 font-semibold hover:text-purple-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">C4</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Cellucor</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Pre-workout #1</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Creadores del pre-entreno más popular del mundo, C4 Original, con más de 2 mil millones de porciones vendidas.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">20 productos</span>
							<button class="text-orange-500 font-semibold hover:text-orange-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">UNI</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Universal Nutrition</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tradición desde 1977</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Una de las marcas más antiguas y respetadas, conocida por Animal Pak y productos hardcore.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">18 productos</span>
							<button class="text-green-500 font-semibold hover:text-green-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">MUT</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Mutant</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Fuerza extrema</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Marca canadiense especializada en productos para atletas que buscan resultados extremos.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">15 productos</span>
							<button class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold hover:text-yellow-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
						<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
								<span class="text-white font-bold">GAT</span>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">GAT Sport</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Rendimiento atlético</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Enfocados en productos de alta calidad para atletas serios y profesionales.</p>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">12 productos</span>
							<button class="text-blue-500 font-semibold hover:text-blue-600">Ver productos →</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Why These Brands -->
		<section class="py-16 bg-gray-900 text-white">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">¿Por Qué Elegimos Estas Marcas?</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Calidad Certificada</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-300">Todas nuestras marcas cuentan con certificaciones GMP, FDA y terceros independientes que garantizan pureza y potencia.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Respaldo Científico</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-300">Cada marca invierte millones en investigación y desarrollo, respaldando sus fórmulas con estudios clínicos.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Resultados Comprobados</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-300">Atletas profesionales y millones de usuarios confían en estas marcas para alcanzar sus objetivos fitness.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	

</PageLayout>
